Each a element must contain text or an img with an alt attribute.

A link name allows screen readers to voice what the links does. If there is no link text or the `alt` text is blank, screen readers have nothing to read, so read out the URL instead. To add a name do one of the following:

  • Add text between the a element start and end tags
  • Add an aria-label attribute
  • Add an aria-labelledby attribute
  • Add an img alt attribute if the link contains an img element

HTML form control has no accessible name.

A label (or name) linked to the control allows screen readers to voice the label correctly when reading the control. To add a label do one of the following:

  • Use a label element with the for attribute set to the ID of the form control
  • Wrap a label element around the form control
  • Add a title attribute
  • Add an aria-label attribute
  • Add an aria-labelledby attribute

1017

HTML form control has no accessible name.

A label (or name) linked to the control allows screen readers to voice the label correctly when reading the control. To add a label do one of the following:

  • Use a label element with the for attribute set to the ID of the form control
  • Wrap a label element around the form control
  • Add a title attribute
  • Add an aria-label attribute
  • Add an aria-labelledby attribute

3180

HTML form control has no accessible name.

A label (or name) linked to the control allows screen readers to voice the label correctly when reading the control. To add a label do one of the following:

  • Use a label element with the for attribute set to the ID of the form control
  • Wrap a label element around the form control
  • Add a title attribute
  • Add an aria-label attribute
  • Add an aria-labelledby attribute
Line 3180 WCAG 2.1 A F68 Section 508 (2017) A F68

3194

The visual label must appear in the accessible name of links and controls.
Visual label: Sale TOTO Neorest NX1 Elongated Dual-Flush Integrated Bidet Seat One-Piece Toilet in Cotton White Model: MS900CUMFG#01 Our Price: $11,021.00 Sale Price: $8,265.75 not in Sale Neorest NX1 Elongated Dual-Flush Integrated Bidet Seat One-Piece Toilet in Cotton White TOTO Neorest NX1 Elongated Dual-Flush Integrated Bidet Seat One-Piece Toilet in Cotton White Model: MS900CUMFG#01 Our Price: $11,021.00 Sale Price: $8,265.75
People who use speech control rely on being able to select elements using the visual label displayed on screen. If this isn't part of the accessible name, they can't select elements by name.
Line 3194 WCAG 2.1 A F96 Section 508 (2017) A F96

Each a element must contain text or an img with an alt attribute.

A link name allows screen readers to voice what the links does. If there is no link text or the `alt` text is blank, screen readers have nothing to read, so read out the URL instead. To add a name do one of the following:

  • Add text between the a element start and end tags
  • Add an aria-label attribute
  • Add an aria-labelledby attribute
  • Add an img alt attribute if the link contains an img element
